0f5itleja! |trans-title=Mighty fighter! |language=Estonian |work=[[\u00d5htuleht]] |accessdate=23 May 2011 |date=23 March 2011}}</ref> He scored his first goal on 14 November 2012 in a [[Exhibition game|friendly]] against [[United Arab Emirates national football team|United Arab Emirates]], putting the ball firmly into the net after receiving a long pass from midfield by [[Konstantin Vassiljev]].\n\n===International goals===\n:''Scores and results list Estonia's goal tally first.''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 14 November 2012 || [[Mohammed Bin Zayed Stadium]], [[Abu Dhabi]] || {{fb|United Arab Emirates}} || '''1'''\u20131 || 1\u20132<br /> || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Club===\n* '''[[FC Valga]]'''\n** [[Esiliiga|Estonian Second Division]]: 2002\n*** Runners Up: 2001\n* '''[[FC Flora Tallinn]]'''\n** [[Meistriliiga|Estonian Top Division]]: 2003\n*** Runners Up: 2007, 2008\n** [[Estonian Cup]]: 2008\n*** Runners Up: 2003, 2006\n** [[Estonian SuperCup]]: 2003, 2004\n*** Runners Up: 2006\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.fcflora.ee/index.php?main_id=11&id=17? Flora FC profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ahjupera, Jarmo}}\n[[Category:1984 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from V\u00f5hma]]\n[[Category:Estonian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Estonia international footballers]]\n[[Category:FC Flora players]]\n[[Category:N\u00f5mme Kalju FC|Players]]\n[[Category:JK Tervis P\u00e4rnu players]]\n[[Category:FC Warrior Valga players]]\n[[Category:Viljandi JK Tulevik players]]\n[[Category:Gy\u0151ri ETO FC players]]\n[[Category:\u00dajpest FC players]]\n[[Category:Nemzeti Bajnoks\u00e1g I players]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Hungary]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Hungary]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Eston