cast\"/>\n*[[James Morrison (actor)|James Morrison]] as Warden Dwight Murphy<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*[[Christopher Murray (actor)|Christopher Murray]] as Officer Olson<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*[[Max Perlich]] as Hank<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*[[Tim Roth]] as Gary \"Hutch\" Hutchens<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*Mary Stofle as Ruth Davenport\n{{div col end}}\n\n'''Supernatural'''\n{{Div col|colwidth=25em}}\n*Phoebe Augustine as American Girl{{efn|name=archnew}}<ref name=\"officialcast\"/><ref name=\"37 characters\"/>\n*[[Monica Bellucci]] as herself<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*[[David Bowie]]{{efn|name=inmemoriam}} as Phillip Jeffries{{efn|name=archive}}<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n**Nathan Frizzell as the voice of Phillip Jeffries<ref>{{cite web |url=https://moviepilot.com/p/twin-peaks-season-3-episode-14-easter-eggs/4348080 |title=6 Things You Might Have Missed In 'Twin Peaks' Season 3, Episode 14 |publisher=Movie Pilot |first=Alexandra |last=Ekstein-Kon |date=August 16, 2017 |accessdate=August 20, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820203627/https://moviepilot.com/p/twin-peaks-season-3-episode-14-easter-eggs/4348080# |archive-date=August 20, 2017 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n*Robert Broski as Woodsman<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*[[Don S. Davis]]{{efn|name=inmemoriam}} as Major [[Garland Briggs]]{{efn|name=archive}}<ref name=\"briggs\">{{cite news|last1=McFarland|first1=Melanie|title=\"I don't understand this situation at all\": Easter egg hunting in \"Twin Peaks\"|url=http://www.salon.com/2017/05/25/i-do-not-understand-this-situation-at-all-easter-egg-hunting-in-twin-peaks/|accessdate=May 26, 2017|work=Salon|date=May 26, 2017}}</ref>\n*Erica Eynon as Experiment<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*[[Sheryl Lee]] as [[Laura Palmer]]<ref name=\"cast\"/><ref name=\"37 characters\"/>\n*[[Joy Nash]] as Se\u00f1orita Dido<ref name=\"officialcast\"/>\n*Carlton Lee Russell as the Jumping Man<ref name=\"officialcast\"/><ref name=\"37 